snippet.title: The Crew 2: S6E2 Dominion Frozen Reveal Trailer | #UbiForward
snippet.description:
It's time for a cool new episode in The Crew 2! Season 6 Episode 2: Dominion Frozen is coming on September 14 as a free update with new cars, new events, and a chilling new kind of challenge: ice tracks.
